@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.abs((wp.sin(tmp + 0.70) + (tmp + 0.53 + v0 + 0.79)))
    v1 = ((0.35 * (v2 + 0.14 + v2 + 0.21)) - (0.08 * wp.exp(v1 + 0.40)))
    v1 = v0
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.abs(wp.cos(tmp + 0.53)))
    v1 = (v0 - wp.exp((v2 + 0.50 - v0 + 0.55)))
    v0 = (0.24 + ((tmp + 0.40 * tmp + 0.35) - (tmp + 0.59 / v0 + 0.01)))
    v0 = v0
    data[tid] = v0
